name: BigBrother-File-System
description: BigBrother FS is a project that involved extending the functionality of a FAT filesystem. We completed essential operations like directory deletion and added features for transparent filesystem activity monitoring. This project sheds light on the flexibility of Unix filesystems and underscores the importance of open-source operating systems.
